---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Disclaimer" description="Read the disclaimer for ODY Spatial's website">
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <article class="prose prose-zinc max-w-none space-y-8">
      <header class="mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900 sm:text-5xl">Website Disclaimer</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-zinc-600"><strong>Last Updated:</strong> January 2, 2025</p>
      </header>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-900">1. General Information</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-zinc-600">
          The information provided on odyspatial.com ("Website") is for general informational purposes only. ODY Spatial ("we," "us," or "our") makes no representation or warranty regarding the accuracy, completeness, or current nature of any information provided.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-900">2. Portfolio and Images</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-zinc-600">
          <li>Project images in our portfolio represent actual completed work</li>
          <li>Images may not exactly reflect current conditions as properties may have been modified after completion</li>
          <li>Color representation may vary depending on your device's display settings</li>
          <li>Some images may be digitally enhanced to better showcase design details</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-900">3. Professional Advice</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-zinc-600">
          <li>Our website content does not constitute professional advice</li>
          <li>All design consultations must be conducted through official channels</li>
          <li>Specific recommendations will only be made after formal engagement</li>
          <li>Online information should not be used as a substitute for professional consultation</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-900">4. Third-Party Content</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-zinc-600">
          <li>Our website may contain links to third-party websites</li>
          <li>We are not responsible for third-party content or services</li>
          <li>Third-party links do not imply endorsement or approval</li>
          <li>Users access third-party content at their own risk</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-900">5. Pricing and Availability</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-zinc-600">
          <li>All pricing is subject to change without notice</li>
          <li>Service availability may vary by location and schedule</li>
          <li>Published rates are in USD and may not include all applicable fees</li>
          <li>Actual project costs will be determined during consultation</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-900">6. Accuracy of Information</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-zinc-600">
          <li>We strive to maintain current and accurate information</li>
          <li>Website content is updated periodically</li>
          <li>No guarantee of real-time accuracy is made</li>
          <li>Users should verify critical information during consultation</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-900">7. User Responsibilities</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-zinc-600">
          <li>Users are responsible for verifying information relevance</li>
          <li>Professional advice should be sought for specific situations</li>
          <li>Users should ensure compliance with local regulations</li>
          <li>Technical specifications should be independently verified</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-900">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-zinc-600">
          <li>We shall not be liable for any:</li>
          <li>Direct, indirect, or consequential losses</li>
          <li>Business or personal decisions made based on website content</li>
          <li>Technical inaccuracies or typographical errors</li>
          <li>Losses arising from website use or inability to use</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>